# Backend conventions

- FastAPI app lives under `app/`; entry: `uvicorn app.main:app`.
- Auth: federated login via `POST /api/auth/login` (google, yahoo, microsoft).
- Persist users in SQLAlchemy `users` table; return `UserResponse` + JWT to frontend.
- Use Pydantic schemas in `app/schemas/`; routes in `app/routers/`.


